manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: JETASU portable mini washing machine How are our portable washing machines different from other portable washing machines? The large capacity of 11.5L can hold more items to be cleanedThe JETASU mini washing machine is an LCD touch screen, and other mini washing machines are all push-button control, which requires hard pressing to start and switch modesCompared to other foldable mini washing machines, we have more power than other washing machines, so the cleaning effect is better and more stable, and there is no shaking at allSave energy, our washing machine only needs 0.01 kWh/h, which can save more energy and costOur washing machines don't need to be painfully assembled when they arrive, they just need to be put on the lid and used directlyOur washing machines are made of TPE and food-grade silicone materials, which are safe and reliable. It is also equipped with a blue light Decontamination function, which will remove all dirt from the cleaning items. It also complies with international safety standards, so consumers can use it with confidence.We have all the functions that others have, and we still have the functions that others don't！

Designed for lazy people JETASU small portable washing machine is easy to operate, just put in the items that need to be washed, then pour 2/3 of the water and the right amount of detergent, press and hold the switch for two seconds to turn on, after washing the clothes, do not need to pour water manually, just put down the tube can automatically drain, during the process you can enjoy playing with your phone or watering the flowersVery suitable for washing socks, underwear, baby clothes, pet clothes, towels, and all other small items, you can continue to be a 'lazy person' forever!

Suitable for a variety of life scenarios! The small size makes it easy to fit in your suitcase, making it the best choice for apartments, dormitories, camping, tours, RVs, truckers, rentals, or temporary accommodation!

When you see piles of items, are you still prepared to wash them by hand in pain? Laundry mixing Personal clothing and socks and underwear are washed separately to protect the health of the family, otherwise it is easy to cross infection causing itchy skin Ordinary hand wash Hand washing is easy to feel the pain of fingers and wrists, and the cleaning effect is poor, inefficient and long-lasting Mountains of socks and underwear Isn't it painful to see mountains of socks and underwear piled up every day? With the JETASU mini washing machine, you can simply throw the items that need to be washed into the washing machine and you can solve your problems!

Simple and easy to use 1. Put laundry in a portable washing machine2Pour two-thirds of the water and laundry detergent into the container3. Press and hold the "Start/Stop" button for 2 seconds to turn the washing machine on or off. Just tap the Start/Stop button to switch between cleaning modes4. Put down the filter pipe, and the wastewater will be discharged automatically5. Put the white drain basket into the washing machine, put the clothes that need to be dehydrated into the white drain basket, and use the dehydration mode to dry and dehydrate (the drain basket in the dehydration mode can keep the clothes moist and not dripping, and the clothes and socks cannot be completely dried, it is recommended to wring them out slightly after washing the clothes and socks and dry them directly)6. Tips: Portable washing machines are not recommended to wash jeans, thick coats, etc
